## Enforcement

**MANDATORY:** This rule applies to:
- All test scripts that run > 30 seconds
- All validation/gate scripts
- All batch processing operations
- All field building operations
- All dataset encoding operations

**Code Review Checklist:**
- [ ] Instructions displayed before long operations?
- [ ] Progress bars with rate/ETA using tqdm?
- [ ] Heartbeat indicator for operations > 2 minutes?
- [ ] Step indicators for multi-step processes?
- [ ] Clear status indicators (working/progressing/hung)?

